    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0023.b016",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Campaign save example",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "On the last page of the sheet, to the right of the Choice Matrix, note any other Map tile numbers ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "relevant to the current Story and Doom",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " cards, as well as all numbers of Map tiles with ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "other game elements",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ", such as tokens and tiles, placed on them (e.g. ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Lab-yrinthian Templemarker",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "), as well as the current position of the ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Adversary",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ".Note the current ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Triskelion",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " stats of each Argonaut on their re-spective Argonaut Sheets.Store your ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Technology deck",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ",",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " Projects deck",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ", ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Argo Armory deck",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ", ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Exploration deck",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ", ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Mnemos Vault",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": ", gained ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Clue cards",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " and all un-locked ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Godform",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " and ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Summoning",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " cards separate from other com-ponents of the same type, to easily access them when you resume your campaign.Place all Explored Map tiles into the Explored Map space in the game insert. ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Important: ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Always remember to put all the Explored Map tiles in this space! During the next game session, you may re-construct the whole Map at the start or only reconstruct the parts relevant for that game session (the Map is big!).",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "If you don’t reconstruct the whole Map, be sure to leave all the unused Explored Map tiles in the Explored Map space in the game insert.",
          "marks": []
        },
