    {
      "kind": "heading",
      "id": "p0023.b017",
      "level": 2,
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Nymph Summonings",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "id": "p0023.b018",
      "children": [
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "During the course of a campaign, you will unlock various mythic allies that can be summoned to turn the tide of Battle or enable game-changing Voyage abilities. As such, the usage of these allies is extremely limited.Each Nymph Summoning has a corresponding tarot-sized Sum-moning card and a matching Summoning token. ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Summoning cardExplored Map space in the game insert",
